text: Chloe George (born Chloe Gasparini) is an American musician. George has written songs with artists including Dua Lipa and Normani. ==Biography== George attended the New York University Tisch School of the Arts. In 2021, George signed to the Fader Label in 2021, where she released her first song called Peachi. George released her debut EP in 2022 called Penny. ==References== Category:New York University alumni Category:Musicians from New York City Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
